  "instructions": [
    "In a large pot, combine wheat and onion.",
    "Add cumin, cinnamon powder, smoked paprika, and salt. Stir well.",
    "Pour in the 1/2 cup of water. Bring to a boil then reduce heat to low.",
    "Simmer for about 5 minutes or until liquid is absorbed.",
    "In another pan, heat oil over medium-high heat.",
    "Add Worcestershire sauce and lemon juice. Stir well until it thickens.",
    "Pour the mixture over wheat mixture in the pot. Add remaining water.",
    "Cover and steam for an additional 10 minutes or until desired consistency is reached."
